1
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:07,375
SEBELUM INI

2
00:00:07,458 --> 00:00:08,750
Dia dah mati! Mari!

3
00:00:11,916 --> 00:00:12,958
Apa…

4
00:00:13,208 --> 00:00:15,041
Tolak ia ke atas…

5
00:00:15,125 --> 00:00:16,875
Awak dari mana?

6
00:00:23,291 --> 00:00:25,916
Dia nak kita bantu dia cari bintang itu.

7
00:00:28,208 --> 00:00:29,458
Nori?

8
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:35,000
Saya perlu pulang ke Dunia Tengah.

9
00:00:35,041 --> 00:00:38,625
Bukan Elf yang usir kami
dari tanah air kami, tapi Orc.

10
00:00:38,708 --> 00:00:40,833
Adakah itu lambang raja orang awak?

11
00:00:40,916 --> 00:00:42,291
Kami tiada raja.

12
00:00:51,916 --> 00:00:54,458
Semua kota kara akan ditutup.

13
00:00:54,541 --> 00:00:56,000
Tengok buat kali terakhir?

14
00:00:56,083 --> 00:00:57,791
Ia dah banyak berubah, Pengawas.

15
00:00:57,875 --> 00:00:59,875
Tapi penghuni di sini masih sama.

16
00:00:59,958 --> 00:01:03,833
Kejahatan masih ada dalam diri mereka
yang menyokong Morgoth.

17
00:01:03,916 --> 00:01:07,500
-Ada orang gali laluan ini.
-Atau sesuatu. Ini bukan kerja manusia.

18
00:03:27,041 --> 00:03:28,125
Teruskannya.

19
00:03:33,458 --> 00:03:36,083
Kamu! Tambat dia.

20
00:03:36,666 --> 00:03:38,291
Humban dia dengan yang lain.

21
00:03:38,375 --> 00:03:41,958
Kau buatlah. Aku dah berjemur
semasa bekerja semalam.

22
00:03:42,041 --> 00:03:46,916
Kalau Adar dah takdirkan kau berjemur
sampai hitam, kau kenalah buat.

23
00:03:47,000 --> 00:03:50,333
Baiklah, kerana Adar, bukan kerana kau!

24
00:03:56,500 --> 00:03:58,916
Demi Adar!

25
00:04:09,458 --> 00:04:11,333
Masa rehat dah tamat, pemalas.

26
00:04:11,416 --> 00:04:12,666
Sekarang, gali.

27
00:05:04,583 --> 00:05:05,625
Dia masih hidup.

28
00:05:15,833 --> 00:05:19,541
Pemilik kapal ini,
penyelamat atau penawan?

29
00:05:20,166 --> 00:05:22,666
Ia tak beracun,
jika itu yang awak bimbangkan.

30
00:05:25,750 --> 00:05:27,166
Tak beracun bagi manusia.

31
00:06:23,416 --> 00:06:26,833
Eldar berada di atas kapal saya?

32
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,541
Pelik sekali.

33
00:06:31,625 --> 00:06:32,958
Kapal apakah ini?

34
00:06:33,041 --> 00:06:36,541
Bertenang. Saya harus menyerahkan awak
kepada orang atasan saya.

35
00:06:36,625 --> 00:06:38,958
Mereka akan jawab semua soalan awak.

36
00:06:39,041 --> 00:06:40,666
Kita menuju ke mana?

37
00:06:41,541 --> 00:06:44,375
Tengoklah sendiri. Kita dah hampir tiba.

38
00:06:45,125 --> 00:06:46,291
Hampir ke mana?

39
00:06:51,125 --> 00:06:52,208
Tanah air.

40
00:07:46,041 --> 00:07:47,458
Tempat apakah ini?

41
00:07:48,916 --> 00:07:51,166
Tak lain dan tak bukan,

42
00:07:51,250 --> 00:07:52,916
Dunia Bintang.

43
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:56,458
Dunia manusia paling barat.

44
00:07:58,125 --> 00:08:02,291
Kerajaan Pulau Númenor.

45
00:08:03,750 --> 00:08:05,000
Perlahankan kapal!

46
00:08:57,916 --> 00:09:00,041
-Itu Elfkah?
-Tak nampak apa-apa…

47
00:09:01,833 --> 00:09:05,041
Sejak bila Manusia macam saya
pandai bina kerajaan sebegini?

48
00:09:07,125 --> 00:09:08,958
Manusia ini bukan macam awak.

49
00:09:11,083 --> 00:09:14,791
Semasa Perang Besar,
nenek moyang awak sokong Morgoth.

50
00:09:15,750 --> 00:09:17,625
Mereka sokong Elf.

51
00:09:18,166 --> 00:09:21,041
Sebagai ganjaran,
Valar anugerahi mereka pulau ini,

52
00:09:21,125 --> 00:09:23,125
yang kini telah banyak berubah.

53
00:09:23,208 --> 00:09:25,500
Bunyinya macam awak iri hati.

54
00:09:26,416 --> 00:09:27,833
Tidak, bukan iri hati.

55
00:09:28,416 --> 00:09:29,541
Dukacita.

56
00:09:30,458 --> 00:09:33,458
Dulu, Elf bebas datang
dan pergi dari sini.

57
00:09:33,541 --> 00:09:35,291
Kami bagaikan bersaudara.

58
00:09:36,083 --> 00:09:39,000
Bertukar-tukar hadiah dan ilmu.

59
00:09:39,083 --> 00:09:40,708
Apa yang berlaku?

60
00:09:40,791 --> 00:09:42,750
Númenor halau kapal kami.

61
00:09:42,833 --> 00:09:44,875
Akhirnya, mereka putuskan hubungan.

62
00:09:44,958 --> 00:09:46,041
Kenapa?

63
00:09:47,666 --> 00:09:49,375
Nanti kita tahulah.

64
00:09:49,458 --> 00:09:50,625
Jangan berhenti.

65
00:09:52,625 --> 00:09:55,333
Kamu tentu tak mahu sesat
di sini tanpa pengiring.

66
00:09:57,500 --> 00:09:59,041
Letak dengan yang lain.

67
00:09:59,666 --> 00:10:00,500
Terlalu panas.

68
00:10:32,291 --> 00:10:34,375
Bawa bersabar.

69
00:10:34,916 --> 00:10:36,916
Kita warga Númenor.

70
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:41,500
Mari kita ketepikan sejarah buat masa ini
dan jaga adab kita.

71
00:10:42,291 --> 00:10:45,000
Jangan cuba cari gaduh dengan mereka.

72
00:10:45,083 --> 00:10:47,416
Kapten. Ratu sedang sibuk.

73
00:10:47,500 --> 00:10:50,041
Begitu juga Canselor Pharazôn.
Lebih baik tuan…

74
00:11:19,416 --> 00:11:20,416
Melutut.

75
00:11:20,791 --> 00:11:22,291
Kami tak melutut di Númenor.

76
00:11:25,166 --> 00:11:26,166
Maaf.

77
00:11:28,708 --> 00:11:30,083
Cakap, Elf.

78
00:11:31,833 --> 00:11:33,000
Siapa nama kamu?

79
00:11:37,708 --> 00:11:39,833
Galadriel daripada suku Noldor.

80
00:11:40,833 --> 00:11:44,375
Anak Wangsa Finarfin.

81
00:11:44,458 --> 00:11:48,500
Komander Tentera Utara Raja Gil-galad.

82
00:11:53,625 --> 00:11:54,833
Halbrand.

83
00:11:55,666 --> 00:11:57,541
Dari Tanah Selatan.

84
00:11:58,125 --> 00:12:00,416
Manusia dan Elf, bersama?

85
00:12:01,000 --> 00:12:02,208
Takdir yang menentukan.

86
00:12:02,291 --> 00:12:05,416
Kami bersama tanpa sengaja
dan bertemu di laut terbuka.

87
00:12:06,250 --> 00:12:09,250
Kapten tuan telah menyelamatkan kami
daripada maut.

88
00:12:10,125 --> 00:12:14,166
Kami cuma berharap
Númenor terus mengasihani kami

89
00:12:14,250 --> 00:12:16,791
dan beri kami kapal untuk ke Dunia Tengah.

90
00:12:20,208 --> 00:12:22,416
Sudah lama kapal Númenor

91
00:12:22,500 --> 00:12:25,375
tak dibenarkan pergi ke sana
bagi pihak Elf.

92
00:12:25,458 --> 00:12:28,875
Kerana Elflah pulau ini dikurniakan
kepada tuan.

93
00:12:28,958 --> 00:12:31,708
Takkanlah tuan tak boleh
beri kami sebuah kapal.

94
00:12:35,125 --> 00:12:37,958
Nenek moyang kami tak dikurniakan apa-apa.

95
00:12:39,666 --> 00:12:43,125
Mereka tumpahkan darah demi pulau ini.

96
00:12:43,208 --> 00:12:44,458
Maksud Elf ini…

97
00:12:44,541 --> 00:12:47,625
Jika darah perlu tumpah, saya rela.

98
00:12:48,541 --> 00:12:50,500
Tapi yang pasti, saya akan ke sana.

99
00:12:51,416 --> 00:12:52,916
Beta alu-alukan cubaan kamu.

100
00:12:53,458 --> 00:12:55,291
Saya tak perlu dialu-alukan.

101
00:12:56,083 --> 00:12:58,791
Kehadiran kamu pun makin tak dialu-alukan.

102
00:12:58,875 --> 00:13:00,541
-Pengawal!
-Kawan-kawan.

103
00:13:02,083 --> 00:13:06,208
Nampaknya niat kami untuk berangkat
menimbulkan beberapa masalah.

104
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:09,333
Mungkin lebih baik jika kami tinggal…

105
00:13:09,416 --> 00:13:13,125
-Tinggal?
-Cukup lama, wahai ratu yang mulia,

106
00:13:13,208 --> 00:13:17,500
untuk tuanku dan penasihat tuanku
mempertimbangkan permintaan kami.

107
00:13:19,458 --> 00:13:21,125
Mungkin selama beberapa hari?

108
00:13:26,000 --> 00:13:30,000
Tiga hari, dan Elf itu
dilarang meninggalkan kawasan istana.

109
00:13:30,083 --> 00:13:31,625
Saya enggan dikurung.

110
00:13:31,708 --> 00:13:33,416
Saya lebih sanggup seksa kuda

111
00:13:33,500 --> 00:13:37,333
daripada mengurung komander
Tentera Utara yang gagah perkasa.

112
00:13:38,958 --> 00:13:41,375
Maka, kamu tetamu Númenor.

113
00:13:48,666 --> 00:13:49,916
Kapten.

114
00:13:52,375 --> 00:13:53,375
Terima kasih.

115
00:14:02,416 --> 00:14:03,791
"Ratu yang mulia?"

116
00:14:04,833 --> 00:14:07,333
Tanah Selatan takkan ke mana-mana.

117
00:14:07,416 --> 00:14:08,583
Penduduknya bagaimana?

118
00:14:08,666 --> 00:14:10,708
Tengoklah. Tempat ini bagaikan syurga.

119
00:14:10,791 --> 00:14:12,208
Kaya dengan jutaan peluang.

120
00:14:12,833 --> 00:14:15,500
Awak ingat saya suka
menempah maut bersama awak?

121
00:14:15,583 --> 00:14:17,833
Awak terjun laut demi seorang.

122
00:14:17,916 --> 00:14:19,250
Saya utamakan ramai orang.

123
00:14:19,333 --> 00:14:22,375
Saya sudah lama mencari ketenangan jiwa.

124
00:14:23,166 --> 00:14:26,583
Tolonglah, demi kebaikan kita,
biarlah saya merasainya.

125
00:14:31,583 --> 00:14:33,833
Mungkin awak juga perlukannya.

126
00:14:45,333 --> 00:14:46,833
Tapi setidak-tidaknya,

127
00:14:48,458 --> 00:14:50,666
janganlah cari musuh baru.

128
00:15:01,041 --> 00:15:03,416
Masalah ini perlu diselesaikan segera.

129
00:15:03,500 --> 00:15:04,666
Dia cuma seorang.

130
00:15:04,750 --> 00:15:07,000
Kerana seorang, dunia boleh huru-hara.

131
00:15:07,750 --> 00:15:10,833
Jangan sampai kita berperang
seperti zaman mantan raja.

132
00:15:12,958 --> 00:15:14,541
Ceritalah tentang kapten itu.

133
00:15:14,625 --> 00:15:16,583
Namanya Elendil.

134
00:15:17,125 --> 00:15:21,166
Berketurunan bangsawan,
kini dia Pengawal Laut dan anak lelakinya,

135
00:15:21,250 --> 00:15:24,625
kalau tak silap,
akan menuruti jejak langkahnya.

136
00:15:26,083 --> 00:15:27,208
Tarik!

137
00:15:28,166 --> 00:15:30,625
Beramai-ramai!

138
00:15:40,500 --> 00:15:41,875
Tarik!

139
00:15:43,583 --> 00:15:47,416
Tarik tali lagi laju
kalau kamu mahu sertai pasukan saya!

140
00:15:48,791 --> 00:15:51,458
Ayuh, kadet!

141
00:15:52,208 --> 00:15:54,166
Beramai-ramai!

142
00:16:02,875 --> 00:16:05,000
Isildur...

143
00:16:05,083 --> 00:16:06,250
Isildur!

144
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:08,083
Isildur!

145
00:16:08,750 --> 00:16:13,416
Kadet yang layak menyertai
angkatan Pengawal Laut

146
00:16:13,500 --> 00:16:17,000
bukan sekadar menjadi pelindung Númenor.

147
00:16:17,083 --> 00:16:18,166
Bukan yang itu!

148
00:16:21,625 --> 00:16:22,750
Imrahil!

149
00:16:22,833 --> 00:16:26,208
Kiri! Bawa ke sebelah kiri!

150
00:16:27,125 --> 00:16:29,208
Valandil! Ontamo!

151
00:16:32,125 --> 00:16:32,958
Tolong! Tarik!

152
00:16:36,875 --> 00:16:39,875
Kerjasama, kadet! Sambung semula!

153
00:16:50,166 --> 00:16:53,708
Tiada panduan lain setegas laut.

154
00:17:33,083 --> 00:17:35,500
Laut sentiasa benar!

155
00:17:36,125 --> 00:17:38,125
Laut sentiasa benar!

156
00:17:42,333 --> 00:17:43,666
Kasihan Imrahil.

157
00:17:44,416 --> 00:17:47,416
Ayahnya mungkin
akan halau dia keluar rumah.

158
00:17:48,125 --> 00:17:49,958
Isil pun sama saja.

159
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:51,833
Saya?

160
00:17:51,916 --> 00:17:55,166
Awak mengelamun sepanjang hari.
Apa masalahnya?

161
00:17:55,250 --> 00:17:57,458
Saya tak sabar keluar belayar. Itu saja.

162
00:17:58,833 --> 00:18:00,833
Sembilan hari lagi!

163
00:18:00,916 --> 00:18:03,916
Kalau lulus Ujian Laut,
dalam empat tahun, kita jadi pegawai.

164
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:05,916
Selepas 10 tahun, kita jadi nakhoda.

165
00:18:06,000 --> 00:18:07,958
-Lagi lapan tahun.
-Rasanya18 tahun.

166
00:18:08,041 --> 00:18:10,166
Isildur! Adik awak datang.

167
00:18:15,708 --> 00:18:16,875
Kamu sampai pun.

168
00:18:17,833 --> 00:18:19,500
Berek, sayang.

169
00:18:19,583 --> 00:18:21,750
Tengoklah, dia tak melukis kali ini.

170
00:18:21,833 --> 00:18:24,500
Kamu tak perlu datang dari jauh
untuk jumpa abang.

171
00:18:24,583 --> 00:18:26,958
-Isil, nak minum?
-Pergilah dulu.

172
00:18:27,041 --> 00:18:29,541
Nanti sertailah kami.
Jangan ikut abang awak.

173
00:18:29,625 --> 00:18:31,583
Nanti awak jadi anak dara tua pula.

174
00:18:31,666 --> 00:18:32,666
Atau anak dara muda.

175
00:18:33,833 --> 00:18:36,916
Kenapa kamu datang? Mana ayah?

176
00:18:43,541 --> 00:18:47,625
Setiawan percaya
kelopak Pohon Putih yang gugur

177
00:18:47,708 --> 00:18:49,375
bukan perkara remeh,

178
00:18:51,083 --> 00:18:54,000
tapi ia titisan air mata Valar.

179
00:18:55,666 --> 00:18:59,333
Satu peringatan bahawasanya
mereka sentiasa memerhati

180
00:19:00,833 --> 00:19:04,708
dan menilai setiap tindak-tanduk kita.

181
00:19:10,500 --> 00:19:12,416
Kamu percayakah kata-kata itu?

182
00:19:12,500 --> 00:19:15,041
Menurut pengalaman patik,
kita tak patut hidup

183
00:19:15,125 --> 00:19:17,916
berdasarkan ramalan dan petanda.

184
00:19:21,750 --> 00:19:25,166
"Elendil." Peliknya nama itu.

185
00:19:26,875 --> 00:19:28,916
Dari pantai barat, bukan?

186
00:19:30,208 --> 00:19:31,416
Ia berasal dari sana.

187
00:19:31,500 --> 00:19:33,208
Apa maknanya?

188
00:19:34,541 --> 00:19:36,125
Lelaki yang sukakan cakerawala.

189
00:19:37,208 --> 00:19:39,625
Bukan itu saja maknanya, bukan?

190
00:19:43,041 --> 00:19:45,250
Dalam bahasa purba Eldar,

191
00:19:45,958 --> 00:19:47,791
ia juga bermakna "rakan Elf."

192
00:19:47,875 --> 00:19:51,125
Ia benarkah? Kamu rakan Elf?

193
00:19:54,666 --> 00:19:57,083
Patik hamba Númenor yang setia.

194
00:19:57,166 --> 00:20:00,875
Namun, walaupun Elf
tak dialu-alukan di pulau kita

195
00:20:00,958 --> 00:20:03,916
sejak pemerintahan nenek moyang beta,

196
00:20:04,000 --> 00:20:07,333
kamu tetap ingkar. Kenapa, ya?

197
00:20:08,166 --> 00:20:10,500
Laut yang membawanya kepada saya,

198
00:20:12,333 --> 00:20:14,000
dan laut sentiasa benar.

199
00:20:15,041 --> 00:20:16,916
Laut tak boleh menderhaka.

200
00:20:22,833 --> 00:20:24,208
Ampun tuanku,

201
00:20:24,875 --> 00:20:28,541
tapi patik cuma ambil tindakan
yang paling wajar ketika itu.

202
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:33,291
Elendil, jika itulah hajat kamu,

203
00:20:35,541 --> 00:20:39,250
maka beta mahu kamu buat sesuatu.

204
00:21:02,916 --> 00:21:04,458
LAUTAN PEMUTUS

205
00:21:08,250 --> 00:21:10,625
TANAH SELATAN

206
00:21:42,166 --> 00:21:44,750
Laluan ini menuju ke Hordern.

207
00:21:46,333 --> 00:21:47,500
Malah, lebih jauh lagi.

208
00:21:48,583 --> 00:21:51,083
Mereka tentu ikut laluan ini
agar tidak dikesan

209
00:21:51,166 --> 00:21:53,583
dan dapat berlindung
daripada cahaya suria.

210
00:21:57,500 --> 00:21:59,416
Mereka mencari sesuatu.

211
00:22:00,791 --> 00:22:02,625
Mungkin sejenis senjata?

212
00:22:02,708 --> 00:22:04,000
Saya tak tahu.

213
00:22:04,708 --> 00:22:07,041
Tapi mereka geledah semua kampung,

214
00:22:07,750 --> 00:22:10,375
setiap malam untuk mencarinya
buat ketua mereka.

215
00:22:10,750 --> 00:22:13,500
Salah seorang Orc sebut tentang tuan

216
00:22:13,583 --> 00:22:17,041
yang mereka sembah,
itu pun kalau Orc tahu menyembah.

217
00:22:17,541 --> 00:22:20,041
Nampaknya Morgoth ada pengganti.

218
00:22:20,875 --> 00:22:21,875
"Adar."

219
00:22:24,333 --> 00:22:27,541
Kenapa Orc guna perkataan Elf
untuk ketua mereka?

220
00:22:27,625 --> 00:22:30,583
Orang kata, Sauron ada banyak nama.

221
00:22:30,666 --> 00:22:32,333
Mungkin ini juga namanya.

222
00:22:32,416 --> 00:22:35,041
Nampaknya ada muslihat
yang kita tak sedari.

223
00:22:36,083 --> 00:22:38,166
Jika ada peluang,

224
00:22:38,250 --> 00:22:40,750
cuba lihat kawasan di atas parit ini.

225
00:22:40,833 --> 00:22:42,458
Cari sempadan hutan terdekat.

226
00:22:42,541 --> 00:22:45,458
Apabila matahari terik,
kita akan lari dari sini.

227
00:22:45,541 --> 00:22:47,625
Kalau ada antara kita berjaya pulang,

228
00:22:47,708 --> 00:22:49,458
kita boleh bawa bala tentera

229
00:22:49,541 --> 00:22:53,041
dan hapuskan musuh dari muka bumi ini.

230
00:22:54,041 --> 00:22:57,791
Tutup mulut dan gali, Elf!

231
00:22:58,375 --> 00:23:01,000
-Akar ini menghalang laluan.
-Cabut sajalah.

232
